<HEADLINE>
Four Killed in Heating System Explosion in Paris
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Paris <TIMEX2 val="2000-11-15" mod="" set="" non_specific="" anchor_val="" anchor_dir="" comment="">11-15</TIMEX2> (AFP) -

A security source said four people were killed and many others were
seriously injured in a heating system explosion <TIMEX2 val="2000-11-15TEV" mod="" set="" non_specific="" anchor_val="" anchor_dir="" comment="">this evening</TIMEX2>
<TIMEX2 val="2000-11-15" mod="" set="" non_specific="" anchor_val="" anchor_dir="" comment="">Wednesday</TIMEX2> in Paris.


The explosion, which happened in an outdoor pit north of the capital,
led to a number of people being buried.
